org.pentaho.di.core
Class BlockingListeningRowSet

java.lang.Object
  org.pentaho.di.core.BlockingListeningRowSet
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<RowSet>, RowSet
public class BlockingListeningRowSet
extends Object
implements Comparable<RowSet>, RowSet

Contains a buffer of rows. Getting rows from the buffer or putting rows in the buffer is synchronized to allow concurrent use of multiple Threads. This class also monitors the idle state of a RowSet

Since:
23-12-2010
Author:
Matt
